        Deprecated. 
        Instantiates a new pdb connector node dialog.
        Parameters:
        config - the configuration
        hasQueryBuilder - Does the node dialog include a query builder?
        runQuery - Does the node execute a query? (If it does, and the node does not have a query builder, then a text box is included for the XML Query to be entered)
        runReport - Does the node run a report?
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if an invalid combination of boolean parameters is supplied
